{"type": "article", "id": 16314, "title": "这个山上小屋，算不上豪华但是让人内心平静", "description": "适合瑜伽爱好者。", "date": "2015-10-21T06:05:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}, {"id": 17478, "name": "塞尔维亚"}, {"id": 17479, "name": "外立面"}, {"id": 17480, "name": "新旧对比"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 146, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702104345WQFUKZOzv8gJE3jM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/19/this-house-merges-traditional-and-contemporary-to-create-a-unique-aesthetic/\" target=\"_blank\">这是一幢位于塞尔维亚的山上小屋</a>，从外立面可以清楚地看到，它一半是现代，一半是传统。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104339lbUiOJIsoPm085V1.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" title=\"宏观\" alt=\"宏观\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>宏观</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t建筑工作室 <span><a href=\"http://www.exestudio.rs/\">EXE Studio</a> </span>为业主设计了这个位于山上的家。这座山的名字叫作 Mount Maljen ，房子位于山顶的一片空地上，周围由树木环绕。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t想象不出出于怎样的需求会在山上安一个家，不过作为休憩的度假小屋也没准。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021043392UI50nEBMavQzdDF.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"320\" title=\"空旷的空地\" alt=\"空旷的空地\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>空旷的空地</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104340y3ExFBQNczVUH7nA.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" title=\"房子有明暗两部分构成\" alt=\"房子有明暗两部分构成\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>房子有明暗两部分构成</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104340DJ6hX129RdlqH0k7.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" title=\"明亮的空间好像很适合做瑜伽\" alt=\"明亮的空间好像很适合做瑜伽\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>明亮的空间好像很适合做瑜伽</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104341TuKniw9kUmhFoMbg.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"沿着楼梯可以走到上面去\" alt=\"沿着楼梯可以走到上面去\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>沿着楼梯可以走到上面去</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104341JPMNmFAEdLzRroUw.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" title=\"古老部分\" alt=\"古老部分\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>古老部分</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104342nVZTgEir1HYJbseK.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"室内装修很温馨\" alt=\"室内装修很温馨\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>室内装修很温馨</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104342O8LE6zaZRINMF4Jt.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" title=\"室内的细节\" alt=\"室内的细节\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>室内的细节</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这个叫作 <a href=\"http://www.exestudio.rs/\">EXE Studio</a> 的建筑工作室完成了不少项目呢，其中包括一些室内装修：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104343m9W8IGjszb1Al4v2.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"512\" title=\"亮片相互呼应\" alt=\"亮片相互呼应\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>亮片相互呼应</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104343oMkQdP1xX3J0jIZF.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"510\" title=\"设计图\" alt=\"设计图\" data-ratio=\"0.796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>设计图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104344iLGy9zWC0ePkr3c1.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"434\" title=\"The Light Box Apartment\" alt=\"The Light Box Apartment\" data-ratio=\"0.678125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>The Light Box Apartment</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021043441PhAWsiIbYtSp38o.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"338\" title=\"The Light Box Apartment\" alt=\"The Light Box Apartment\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>The Light Box Apartment</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021043447JgQay3iqYrhsVUR.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"353\" title=\"医生的诊所\" alt=\"医生的诊所\" data-ratio=\"0.5515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>医生的诊所</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/19/this-house-merges-traditional-and-contemporary-to-create-a-unique-aesthetic/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}